elements.name: User can access information about the uploaded No Template Control report.

steps.name: I am a logged in user
I navigate to the Clia Labs page
I click on "No Template Control" under "MoCha"
I enter "SC_YQ111" in the search field on "No Template Control" under "MoCha"
I collect information about the sample variant report
I click on the sample control link
I verify that I am on the sample control page for that molecularId
I verify all the values on the left hand side section under "No Template Control"
I verify all the values on the right hand side section under "No Template Control"
I verify all the headings on the "left" hand side section under "No Template Control"
I verify all the headings on the "right" hand side section under "No Template Control"
I verify the presence of SNVs, CNVs and Gene Fusions Table
I verify the valid Ids are links in the SNVs/MNVs/Indels table under "No Template Control"
I verify the valid Ids are links in the Gene Fusions table under "No Template Control"
I verify the valid Ids are links in the Copy Number Variants table under "No Template Control"
